 adjustable and its structure is resolvable\nup to $R_\\lambda \\approx 8000$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jan 2014 16:30:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2014 16:10:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Jul 2014 20:54:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
