tutes the majority of travellers. If instead traveling is dominated by\nthe more social class, our model predicts the existence of an optimal\nacross-groups mixing that maximises the pandemic potential of the disease,\nwhereas the impact of variations in the activity of each group is less\nimportant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jan 2014 19:15:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-01-21"}
