y a linear deformation of\nthe Poisson bracket. The reason why linear deformation of Poisson bracket is\nrequired here is that the noncommutative parameters (which are fields) are\nconstant (they are coming from central and noncentral abelian extensions of\nkinematical groups).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2014 08:06:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-01-22"}
