istribution of surface magnetic fields, and that local field\nstrengths grow with rotation even in stars in which the average field is\nalready saturated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2014 10:14:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-05"}
